::Killfest/Scyther/Incarcinator/Slayer/Crater/Neody::

Killfest walks up to Kali, looking around. "You should have some of your drones load the wounded into shuttles," he says, pointing to a bloody form laying on a scorched hill, Crater, "They're dying out there."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Scyther makes sure Demise and EndBringer are layed in the shuttle, and then enters it. "Ok, lets go to the Trainer base," he says to whoever is piloting it.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Incarcinator reaches a large group of Preds, slowing down and looking around. "Did the Trainer get away?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Slayer looks down at Ignatius as the bot stirs, raising an eyebrow at his words. Looked like Ignatius took a bit too many shots to the head.

"That's what I'm doing," he replies, continuing to fly, now clear of land and Preds. "Anywhere particular you want to go?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Crater passes out from mech fluid loss, his last sight being the destroyed Trainer base half a mile ahead of him. A trail of mech fluid runs down the hill that he was laying on.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Neody's two pods don't report any danger, and he turns around, walking toward the Destron base, his body aching.
